GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 18th April, 2010
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 18th April, 2010
Shri Shashi Tharoor relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the
Ministry of External Affairs.
